quran[112]{c,v,t}:
  21,1,Karab troh watee bak manusia Peugot keunira dijih ngon Allah Mantong cit dijih jipeubuet laen Mantong jipaleng lalee that Ieupah
  21,2,Peue-peue nyang teuka ayat bak Po jih Nyang baro dijih jideungo sudah Jipeuileh ngon jimeu‘en-meuʻen
  21,3,Ate jih dum nyan lale sileupah Awaknyan lalem jimeurahsia Peue nyan jijakba meunan jipeugah Jih kon insan cit saban ngon gata Jibalek matateuh mangat salah Ka ta eu sihe cit keu noe jiba Pakon cit gata harokteuh leupah
  21,4,Neukheun Tuhan lon neuteupeue keudroe Di langet bumoe peue nyang jipeugah That deuh Neudeungo lom that Neuteupeue
  21,5,Bah haba lumpoe jikheun beurakah Jipeuna-peuna atra nyan bandum Carong meupanton jih nyan jipeugah Yue ba treuk keunoe saboh mukjizat Nyang jeuet keu ayat nyang kon beurakah Lagee dum Rasul yoh masa dilee
  21,6,Ureueng nyan dilee binasa sudah Oh Iheueh jilakee han jimeuiman Nyoe ek jiiman teuma jipeugah
  21,7,Dum Rasul Kamoe yoh gohlom gata Wahyu cit geuba Kamoe peurintah Ureueng agam cit bandum ureueng nyan Teuma tatanyong bak ureueng ceudah Meunyo gata dum hana tateupeue Bak ureueng teupeue tatanyong bagah
  21,8,Kon gopnyan hana pajoh makanan Meupeujeuet gopnyan tuboh ngon gapah Lom pih kon gopnyan ureueng nyang keukai
  21,9,Kamoe bri beukai nyang beuna leupah Lheueh nyan meupeutroh janji ngon gopnyan Bandum ureueng nyan Kamoe peuleupah Meunan pih laen soe nyang h‘eut Kamoe Nyang bantah Kamoe binasa sudah Nyang batat tungang Meupubinasa
  21,10,Teuma keu gata Meupeutron sudah Meupeutron kitab nyang jroh keu gata Pakon digata han tatem papah Peue han tapike ngon akai gata
  21,11,Padum na nyang ka binasa sudah Nanggroe nyang lalem Meupubinasa Meugantoe teuma kaom nyang ceudah Kaom nyang laen di likot jih nyan
  21,12,Teuma keu jih nyan azeueb that leupah ‘Oh ban jirasa azeueb Kamoe bri Jiplueng berlari teumakot leupah
  21,13,Bek kaplueng keunan kajak weh keudeh Bak nyang uroejeh udepkeuh mewah U rumoh dilee keudeh kajak woe Gata nyang jinoe mangat kapeugah
  21,14,Jikheun ceulaka keubit dum kamoe Lalem that kamoe masa nyang sudah
  21,15,Meunankeuh sabe jilakee-lakee Hingga jih lagee jeundrang tho leupah Kamoe peujeuet jih lagee naleueng tho
  21,16,Nyang Kamoe ato dum kon beurakah Langet ngon bumoe ngon bandum asoe Kamoe peujeuet nyoe kon tan phaedah Kon Kamoe peujeuet keu gura-gura
  21,17,Meunyo cit hawameuh that-that mudah Meu napsu Kamoe keu gura-gura Kamoe keurija hana peue salah
  21,18,Teutapi Kamoe Meurhom ngon nyang got Ateueh nyang jeuheut kakeuh jih bicah Gadoh nyang jeuheut gata ceulaka Tapeugah khaba nyang kon keu Allah
  21,19,Soe nyang di langet ngon nyang di bumoe Bandum atra nyoe milek droe-Neuh sah Nyang na di sideh dum malaikat Pubuet ibadat sabe keu Allah Teukabo hana hek geuh pih hana
  21,20,Teuseubeh teuma sabe di babah Malam ngon uroe hana geupiyoh Teuseubeh sunggoh geupujoe Allah
  21,21,Peue le that tuhan sinoe di bumoe Jipeugot keudroejih dum le leupah Ureueng nyang mate jeuet jipeuudep Jeuet jipeubangket teuma jibalah
  21,22,Get pih di langet got pih di bumoe Meunyo le sinoe tuhan jipeugah Nyang bukon Allah dum le di sinoe Meunyo bit meunoe anco dum bicah Tuhan dum laen meunyo le sinoe Langet ngon bumoe reuloh meuruah Tuhan po ‘arasy Maha Suci that Kon sagai meuhat lagee jih peugah
  21,23,Peue nyang Neupeubuet hana soe tanyong Bak jih geutanyong pakon ka salah
  21,24,Peue jicok laen dum jih keu Tuhan Jipeugot tuhan nyang bukon Allah Takheun toh daliteuh dum di gata Jinoe beu sigra laju tapeugah Nyoe kitab bak lon get kitab dilee Bandum nyan teuntee hana geupeugah Geupeugah bandum haba peuingat Keu bandum umat beuna ngon salah Tapi le that jih hana jiteupeue Jicok nyang bateue nyang hak jikeubah
  21,25,Dum Rasul Kamoe yoh gohlom gata Bandum geujak ba peue nyang peurintah Nyang Kamoe wahyu ubak ureueng nyan Tan laen Tuhan meulengkan Allah Bandum nyang laen kon sagai Tuhan Lonkeuh nyang Tuhan nyang beu taseumah
  21,26,Jipeugah aneuk-Neuh malaikat Maha suci that na aneuk Allah Akan tetapi dum malaikat Nyang mulia that dum hamba Allah
  21,27,Tan dilee gopnyan ngon narit Tuhan Peurintah Tuhan geupubuet bagah
  21,28,Tuhan Neuteupeue nyang di keue gopnyan Di likot gopnyan hana meuubah o Chupeuʻat keu gob hanjeuet geulakee Meu kon ka teuntee nyang ridha Allah Teumakotgeuh that bandum keu Tuhan Meubacut pih tan lawan peurintah
  21,29,Beurangsoe nyang kheun lam kawan jih nyan Lon nyoekeuh Tuhan kon sidroe Allah Nyan Kamoe balah keu jih nuraka Soe nyang elanya nyan keueh beunalah
  21,30,Peue di si kaphe hana jiteupeue Langet ngon bumoe rapat that leupah Dilee meukeumat lagee teupatroe Teuma ‘oh dudoe Kamoe peupisah Bandum nyang udep Meupeujeuet bak ie Meunyo hana ie cit jeuet keu sosah Teuma boh pakon han jimeuiman
  21,31,Meupeujeuet gunong raya ngon meugah Meunyo di bumoe Meupeujeuet gunong Han that meuguncang ‘oh na mushibah Meupeujeuet jalan dum dalam bumoe Keudeh ngon keu noe jeuet jijak bagah
  21,32,Meupeujeuet langet sang lagee loteng Lagee bubong seng Meujaga leupah y Bandum tanda nyan dijih jipaleng Jingieng ho laen sang-sang beurakah
  21,33,Tuhan nyang peujeuet malam ngon uroe Ngon mata uroe hu meujeureulah Meunan pih buleven jijak jalan droe Maseng jak keudroe hana soe papah
  21,34,Hana nyang keukai dum manusia Yoh gohlom gata keukai meukeubah Peue jih ek keukai ‘oh mate gata
  21,35,Bandum jirasa mate han ubah Nyang na meunyawong jirasa mate Kamoe nyang uji beuna ngon salah r Jeuheut deungon got dum Kamoe ujoe Bak Kamoe tawo cit teuma bagah
  21,36,‘Oh jieu gata le awak kaphe Jipeukhem teuh le jikheun beurakah Nyoeroh jih nyang kheun keu tuhan tanyoe Bandum jih cit nyoe kaphe keu Allah
  21,37,Cit ka Geupeujeuet dum manusia Napsu keu sigra dumpeue beu bagah Cit Lon peuleunmah bak bandum gata Ayat Lon tanda azeueb that leupah Bek roe talakee beu bagah teuka
  21,38,Toh janji gata laju jipeugah © Í Peue nyang tajanji pajan troh teuka f Meunyo bit beuna peue nyang tapeugah
  21,39,Meunyo jiteupeue dum le si kaphe Watee han ek le droe jipeusiblah 7 Apui bak muka ngon apui bak rueng Hana soe tulong jih nyan jipeuglah
  21,40,Azeueb cit teuka hana jithee-thee Ban tanjo jithee teukeujot leupah Han ek jitulak ‘oh teuka azeueb Tanggoh pih hanjeuet keu jih geupeugah
  21,41,Rasul nyang dilee dum nibak gata 3 Pih jipeuseunda jikhem meuhah-hah 5 Geubri treuk azeueb keu jih nyan teuma Nyang jipeuseunda masa nyang sudah
  21,42,Takheun soe nyang ek jagateuh dum nyan Bak azeueb Tuhan nyang Maha Murah Malam ngon uroe ek na soe jaga Tapi jih nyata han cit meuubah Han cit jiingat dijih keu Pojih Muka jih dijih jipaleng bagah
  21,43,Peue na le tuhan laen dum dijih Nyang peulahra jih bak azeueb Allah Han ek soe bantu jih nibak Kamoe G Meunyo kon Kamce nyang ek jak peuglah Hana meusidroe nyang ek peungon jih
  21,44,Tapi dilee jih cit seunang leupah Kamoe bri seunang jih ngon du-dujih ; Hingga umu jih panyang trep leupah Peue hana jieu bumoe bak jih duek Ka Kamoe peuseuk bineh meutarah Kamoe peukureueng bineh-binehjih Peue mantong cit jih meunang jipeugah
  21,45,Takheun gata dum nyang lon peuingat Wahyu Hadharat kon droe lon peugah Teuma si tuloe meu tapeuingat Hana manfaat meu ube seupah Han deuh jideungo ‘oh tameuhoi jih
  21,46,"Troh azeueb keu jih meubaro teulah : ‘Oh keunong bacut azęueb ubak jih Nibak Tuhan jih ka apoh apah Jikheun ceulaka geutanyo jinoe Taelanya droe masa nyang sudah"
  21,47,Kamoe ba treuk ceng uroe kiamat Nyang ade that-that han tom meusalah Hana meusidroe pih meuelanya Meuube seuma hana meuilah Bahle bacut that leumah di sinoe Keunira Kamoe cukop that leupah s
  21,48,Ka Iheueh Kamoe bri bak nabi Musa Ngon Harun duageuh ba peurintah Kamoe bri kitab ngon peuneurangan Ngon peuringatan mangat bek salah Soe nyang takwa jitueng teuladan j
  21,49,"Takot keu Tuhan nyang Maha Murah À: Bah han deuh geu-eu gopnyan teumakot Bandum geuturot peue nyang peurintah Teumakot geuh lom uroe kiamat"
  21,50,Nyoekeuh amanat beureukat leupah č Nyoe peuringatan nyang Kamoe peutron Pakon gata dum han tatem papah Pakon taungki digata dum nyoe
  21,51,Dilee di-Kamoe pih ka meupeugah Ka heueh Meubri nyoe ubak Ibrahim Gopnyan that yakin peutunyok Allah Kamoe Meuteupeue bandum hai gopnyan
  21,52,Bak watee gopnyan geukheun bak ayah Geukheun bak ayahgeuh ngon bak kaom f Geuh peue nyoe patong dum tajak seumah
  21,53,Jikheun kamoe eu dum du-du kamoe Bandum atra nyoe dilee geuseumah
  21,54,Geukheun nyan gata ngon du-du gata y í Leupah that nyata ka sisat leupah X
  21,55,Jikheun peue beuna nyan nyang gata ba d Kon pura-pura narit tapeugah
  21,56,Geukheun Po gata nyang keubit jinoe Po langet bumoe Neupeujeuet sudah Lon nyoe keu saksi atra nyan bandum Ka Neubri maklum bak lon le Allah
  21,57,Demi Allah lon meupeubinasa € Dum patong gata nyang gata seumah ó Meunyo ka tajak bandum u lua
  21,58,Geupeubinasa treuk laju bagah Patong nyang rayok geukeubah saboh Nyang laen geuproh hana geukeubah Mangat jitanyong teuma bak jih nyan
  21,59,Jikheun treuk soe nyan jeuheut sileupah Q Soe dum peulaku tuhan geutanyoe ; Lalem that jih nyoe hana ban peugah
  21,60,Kheun treuk awak nyan na aneuk muda Jikheun beurhala jimeung peubicah Aneuk muda nyan nan jih Ibrahim
  21,61,Boh mangat yakin jak eu jih bagah Mangat trang jieu le manusia Bek sang duseuta meunan jipeugah
  21,62,Jikheun nyo gata pubuet atra nyoe Ibrahim peue roe buetteuh brok leupah Tuhan dum kamoe tapeubinasa
  21,63,Geukheun nyang raya nyan nyang peubicah Bak tuhan rayok tatanyong laju Meunyo jimeusu mangat jipeugah
  21,64,Teuingat jih treuk bak droe jih bandum Bit gata bandum lalem that leupah
  21,65,Teuma jibalek jiteukui ulee Atra ka tathee teuma jipeugah s Atra cit tathee han jeuet jimarit
  21,66,Meu han jeuet marit peue cit taseumah Geukheun taseumah nyang bukan tuhan Meubacut pih tan jibri phaedah Meularat pih han jibri keu gata
  21,67,‘Euh bit ceulaka gata dum teulah Lom nyang taseumah nyang bukan Tuhan Peue tan pikeran gata nyang ceudah
  21,68,Kheun treuk awak nyan katot jih keudeh C Jijak peujayeh peue nyang taseumah Meu bit tapeubuet tatulong tuhan Teutot jih rijang lam apui mirah
  21,69,Kamoe kheun sijuek dikah hai apui Beu kapeureului ureueng tan salah i Ibrahim teuma ka keuh seulamat
  21,70,Nyang keunong laknat kaphe seurakah Ibrahim jimeung elanya le jih Kamoe peujeuet jih nyang rugoe leupah
  21,71,Gopnyan deungon Luth Kamoe ba jinoe c Keudeh bak bumoe nyang raya tuah Meubri beureukat dalam nanggroe nyan Keu bandum alam nyang got that leupah
  21,72,Meubri keu gopnyan Ishak ngon Yaʻkob $ Aneuk nyang patot geunantoe ayah Bandum ureueng nyan ureueng nyang shaleh
  21,73,Kamoe peuleubeh meutamah tuah Bandum ureueng nyan peumimpin ummat Peutunyok rakyat geuba peurintah i Wahyu bak Kamoe bandum geujak ba Geuyue keurija buet nyang jroh leupah Peubuet seumbahyang geubri ngon zakeuet Bandum geusujud Kamoe geuseumah
  21,74,Ubak nabi Luth hikeumah Meubri Ileum‘ee lagi Kamoe bri luah Meupeuglah gopnyan bak naggroe jeuheut Teumpat jipeubuet jahe sileupah Fasek ngon jeuheut kaom di sinan
  21,75,Meuba treuk gopnyan lam rahmat Allah ; Lam rahmat Kamoe Meupeulop gopnyan l Jeuet teuma gopnyan shaleh that leupah
  21,76,Nabi Noh teuma geumeungadu droe Dilee bak Kamoe haigeuh geupeugah Kamoe teurimong nyang lakee gopnyan Ngon ahli gopnyan Kamoe peusiblah Bak bala raya meupeuglah gopnyan
  21,77,Meutulong gopnyan bak kaom jadah Kaom nyang han tem iman keu Kamoe ja Dum ayat Kamoe sulet jipeugah Kaom nyan jeuheut han jimeuiman Kamoe peukaram treuk dum jih sudah
  21,78,Daud Sulaiman watee geuhukom Tanaman kaom kameng jak reupah PÀ D Pakri geuhukom awak nyan teuma Kamoe peunyata Meukalon sudah
  21,79,Kamoe peumuphom ubak Sulaiman 65 Bandua gopnyan ureueng meutuah Padum hikeumah dengan ‘eleumee Bak gopnyan teuntee Kamoe bri luah Jikheun teuseubeh gunong ngon cicem Ngon Daud jitem Kamoe peumudah Kuasa Kamoe meupeubuet meunan
  21,80,Buet jaroe gopnyan pih keubit ceudah Geupeugot bajee Kamoe peurunoe Nyan bajee beusoe nyang kong that leupah Mangat dalam prang gata bek luka Teuma na gata chukor keu Allah
  21,81,Sulaiman teuma Kamoe bri angen r Jijak peumeuʻen ho nyang geupeugah 3 Bak nanggroe nyang ka meubri beureukat Laju beurangkat keunan geulangkah Cit Kamoe teupeue bandum peukara
  21,82,Lam laot raya chethan dum geukrah Jilangue jinom keudeh lam laot Bandum jipeubuet ban nyang geupeugah Buet-buet nyang laen lom jikeurija Kamoe meujaga bandum bek salah
  21,83,Di Ayyub teuma yoh geungadu droe i Meularat lon nyoe hana ban peugah Droe-Neuh geumaseh han teukira Bandum hana sa ngon gaseh Allah
  21,84,Peue nyang geulakee Kamoe teurimong Luka ngon keumong puleh le bagah Kamoe peugadoh meularat gopnyan Ngon ahli gopnyan Meupeuwo sudah Kamoe bri laen lom ahli gopnyan Nyang saban ngon nyan rahmat meulimpah Bandum atra nyan Kamoe bri rahmat Soe nyang ibadat meunan meubalah
  21,85,"Ismail, Idris deungon Zulkifli Ò; Bandum Kamoe bri saba that leupah"
  21,86,Kamoe peutamong lam rahmat Kamoe Bandum ureueng nyoe shaleh meutuah
  21,87,Nyang Zunnun teuma beungeh that gopnyan Keu kaom gopnyan hana ban peugah Geukeubah kaomgeuh geujak sidroe Geusangka Kamoe han ek meuhilah Sang-sang Kamoe nyoe hana kuasa Lam seupot buta geumeuhoi Allah Tan Tuhan laen meulengkan droe-Neuh Suci that Droe-Neuh lon lalem leupah
  21,88,Kamoe teurimong nyang lakee gopnyan Meupeuglah gopnyan hana le sosah Soe nyang meuiman taʻat keu Kamoe Meunankeuh Kamoe sabee meupeuglah
  21,89,Di Zakaria pih geungadu droe Tuhanku lon nyoe bek Neubri sosah Sidroe lon sagai aneuk lon hana Nyang tueng pusaka Neubri ya Allah Droe-Neuhkeuh nyang ek bri wareh keu lon
  21,90,Kamoe teurimong teuma le bagah Kamoe bri Yahya teuma keu gopnyan Peurumoh gopnyan Kamoe bri tuah Ureueng nyan bandum ubak buet nyang got Laju geuseutot meubagah-bagah Galak meudoʻa gopnyan bak Kamoe Keu ‘azeueb Kamoe teumakot leupah Galak ngon takot ngon khusyu‘ pih that
  21,91,Sidroe treuk meuhat inong meutuah Geupeulahra that meunalee gopnyan Kamoe pruh keunan roh Kamoe bagah Meupeujeuet gopnyan ngon aneuk gopnyan Mukjizat sinan raya that leupah Jeuet saboh tanda keu bandum alam
  21,92,Gata roe bandum hana meupisah Ummat gata dum cit saboh ummat Po gata meuhat cit Lon nyoe Allah Keu Lonkeuh bandum peubuet ibadat Lon sidroe meuhat nyang beu taseumah
  21,93,Teuma awak nyan ka jimeukoh-koh Meuputoh-putoh meupeucah-peucah Jiwoe cit teuma bandum bak Kamoe
  21,94,‘Oh troh bak Kamoe bandum meubalah Soe nyang peubuet got lon jimeuiman Usaha jih nyan méuguna leupah Han sia-sia usaha jih nyan Kamoe tuleh nyan bandum meukeubah
  21,95,Nanggroe nyang ka lheueh Meupeubinasa Jiwoe dum teuma keudeh bak Allah Han mungken jih han jiwoe bak Kamoe
  21,96,Hingga troh sampoe watee geupeuhah Geupeuhah guha Yakjuj wa makjuj Jitron kon bacut rame jih leupah
  21,97,Teuma ka rap troh janji nyang beuna Teuglong dum mata watee nyan teuhah Mata dum kaphe watee nyan teuglong Seurta ngon jikheun ceulaka sudah Wahe ceulaka bandum gata nyoe Dilee atra nyoe dum tapeubeu-ah Hana tapike keu troh atra nyoe Tapi gata nyoe lalem that leupah
  21,98,Nyoe gata bandum due ju nuraka Ngon nyang tapuja nyang bukan Allah Peue nyang taseumah pih sinan sapat Ngon gata meuhat lam apui mirah
  21,99,Meunyo jih Tuhan han jilop keunan Nyoe bandum sinan keukai geukeubah
  21,100,Ngon meusu naph‘ah raya meugr‘o-gr‘o í Han deuh jideungo peue nyang tapeugah
  21,101,Teuma ureueng nyang dilee peubuet got € Gopnyan jioh that ngon apui mirah
  21,102,Meung naph‘ah apui han deuh geudeungo Dalam istanageuh seunang leupah Peue nyang h‘eut napsugeuh na di sinan Keukai geuh sinan seunang ngon mewah
  21,103,Haro hara that raya watee nyan Tapi ureueng nyan han jeuet keu sosah 4 Geusambot gopnyan le malaikat Nyoekeuh pat teumpat gata geukeubah Peue nyang geujanji dilee keu gata Uroe nyoe teuka hana meuubah
  21,104,Uroe nyoe langet dum Kamoe gulong Lagee geugulong surat keureutah Lagee dilee phon yoh Kamoe peujeuet Jinoe meunan jeuet meuwoe seujarah Ka Kamoe janji meunan meupeubuet
  21,105,Lam kitab zabur pih Kamoe peugah Lam kitab zabur ka Kamoe tuleh Oh Iheueh meutuleh peue nyang peurintah Bumoe nyoe teuma jitueng pusaka Bandum le hamba nyang pantah tiwah Hamba nyang shaleh teuʻoh peutimang
  21,106,Atra nyan peusan tapeutroh bagah Peusan keu kaom nyang tem ibadat
  21,107,Gata cit meuhat rahmat meulimpah Meukirem gata cit jeuet keu rahmat Mangat seulamat dum hamba Allah Seuluroh alam meuteumee rahmat
  21,108,Takheun amanat teuma Lon peugah Neuwahyu bak lon Tuhan dum gata Cit sidroe sahja nyan Tuhan Allah Teuma peue gata ka tapeujok droe
  21,109,Meu han jijok droe teuma tapeugah Lon ka lon peutroh saban ngon gata Pajan troh masa nyang janji Allah Han ek lon tujan toe got pih jioh Saleh pajan troh hana Neupeugah
  21,110,Tuhan Neuteupeue narit nyang lahe Nyang hana lahe pih hana ubah Peue-peue nyang tasom bandum Neuteupeue
  21,111,Lom han lon teupeue peue nyoe fitnah i Cubaankeuh nyoe Neubri keu gata Dum got pih gata nak seunang leupah Dang-dang troh watee neubri that seunang
  21,112,Nabi lom neukheun wahe ya Allah Neubri putosan nyang beuna jinoe Tuhan Po kamoe nyang Maha Murah Tuhan nyang tulong kamoe meuteuntee Kon sagai lagee nyang gata peugah AL-HAJJ (EK HAJI) Ngon nama Allah lon peuphon surat Tuhan Hadharat nyang Maha Murah ; Tuhanku Sidroe geumaseh that-that Donya akhirat rahmat Neulimpah